<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HotelScope — ホテル市場調査システム 紹介資料</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&display=swap');

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    width: 297mm;
    height: 210mm;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #eef2f7;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'Yu Gothic', sans-serif;
  }

  .page {
    width: 297mm;
    height: 210mm;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 68mm 1fr;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .left {
    background: linear-gradient(170deg, #0d1b2e 0%, #142847 55%, #1b3561 100%);
    padding: 9mm 7.5mm 8mm;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .glow1 { position: absolute; top: -15mm; right: -12mm; width: 50mm; height: 50mm; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56,132,255,.3) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; }
  .glow2 { position: absolute; bottom: 5mm; left: -10mm; width: 42mm; height: 42mm; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(139,92,246,.2) 0%, transparent 70%); border-radius: 50%; pointer-events: none; }

  .brand { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .brand-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 2mm; background: rgba(56,132,255,.18); border: 1px solid rgba(56,132,255,.4); border-radius: 5px; padding: 1.2mm 3mm; margin-bottom: 4.5mm; }
  .brand-badge span { font-size: 2.6mm; font-weight: 700; color: #60a5fa; letter-spacing: .06em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  h1 { font-size: 9.5mm; font-weight: 900; color: #fff; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: 2mm; }
  h1 em { color: #3b82f6; font-style: normal; }
  .brand-desc { font-size: 2.9mm; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 5mm; }
  .brand-tag { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #3b82f6, #6366f1); color: #fff; font-size: 2.4mm; font-weight: 700; padding: 1.2mm 3.5mm; border-radius: 20px; letter-spacing: .04em; }

  .flow { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .sec-label { font-size: 2.2mm; color: #475569; font-weight: 500; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .1em; margin-bottom: 3.5mm; }
  .flow-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.8mm; }
  .flow-step { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2.5mm; }
  .fd { width: 5.5mm; height: 5.5mm; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 3mm; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .fd.b { background: rgba(59,130,246,.18); border: 1.5px solid #3b82f6; }
  .fd.g { background: rgba(34,197,94,.18); border: 1.5px solid #22c55e; }
  .fd.a { background: rgba(251,191,36,.18); border: 1.5px solid #fbbf24; }
  .fd.p { background: rgba(168,85,247,.18); border: 1.5px solid #a855f7; }
  .ft { font-size: 2.6mm; color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.45; }
  .ft strong { color: #f1f5f9; font-weight: 600; display: block; }
  .fa { width: 1px; height: 2.5mm; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #334155, transparent); margin-left: 2.5mm; }

  .lfoot { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .pills { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5mm; margin-bottom: 2.5mm; }
  .pill { background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: #94a3b8; font-size: 2.1mm; padding: .7mm 2mm; border-radius: 4px; }
  .url-line { font-size: 2.4mm; color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 500; }

  .right { background: #f0f4f9; padding: 7mm 8mm; display: grid; grid-template-rows: auto auto 1fr auto; gap: 4mm; overflow: hidden; }

  .rh { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: space-between; gap: 4mm; }
  .rh-title { font-size: 4mm; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; line-height: 1.3; }
  .rh-title em { color: #3b82f6; font-style: normal; }
  .rh-sub { font-size: 2.6mm; color: #64748b; margin-top: 1mm; line-height: 1.5; }
  .client-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1b2e, #1b3561); color: #fff; border-radius: 7px; padding: 2.5mm 4mm; text-align: right; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .cb-label { font-size: 1.9mm; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: .5mm; }
  .cb-name { font-size: 3mm; font-weight: 700; }
  .cb-role { font-size: 1.9mm; color: #60a5fa; }

  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 3.5mm; overflow: hidden; }
  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 3.5mm; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.8mm; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06); overflow: hidden; position: relative; }
  .card-bar { height: .9mm; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; }
  .bar-blue { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#3b82f6,#60a5fa); }
  .bar-green { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#22c55e,#4ade80); }
  .bar-amber { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#f59e0b,#fbbf24); }
  .bar-purple { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#8b5cf6,#a78bfa); }
  .bar-rose { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#f43f5e,#fb7185); }
  .bar-cyan { background: linear-gradient(90deg,#06b6d4,#22d3ee); }
  .card-head { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2mm; margin-top: 1mm; }
  .ci { font-size: 4.5mm; line-height: 1; }
  .ct { font-size: 2.9mm; font-weight: 700; color: #0f172a; }
  .cd { font-size: 2.2mm; color: #64748b; line-height: 1.5; }
  .ci-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .9mm; }
  .ci-row { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 1.5mm; font-size: 2.1mm; color: #374151; line-height: 1.4; }
  .ci-row::before { content: '▸'; color: #3b82f6; font-size: 1.9mm; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: .2mm; }
  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1mm; margin-top: auto; }
  .tag { font-size: 1.9mm; font-weight: 600; padding: .5mm 2mm; border-radius: 4px; }
  .tbl { background:#dbeafe; color:#1d4ed8; }
  .tgn { background:#dcfce7; color:#15803d; }
  .tam { background:#fef3c7; color:#b45309; }
  .tpu { background:#ede9fe; color:#7c3aed; }
  .tro { background:#ffe4e6; color:#be123c; }
  .tcy { background:#cffafe; color:#0e7490; }
  .tgr { background:#f1f5f9; color:#475569; }

  .sites-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr) 3fr; gap: 3mm; align-items: center; }
  .site-box { background: #fff; border-radius: 7px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 2mm 2.5mm; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.05); }
  .site-icon { font-size: 4.5mm; display: block; line-height: 1.3; }
  .site-name { font-size: 2mm; font-weight: 700; color: #1e293b; display: block; margin-top: .5mm; }
  .site-status { font-size: 1.7mm; font-weight: 600; padding: .4mm 1.5mm; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block; margin-top: .5mm; }
  .s-live { background:#dcfce7; color:#166534; }
  .s-soon { background:#fef3c7; color:#92400e; }

  .roadmap { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fef9c3, #fff7ed); border: 1px solid #fde047; border-radius: 7px; padding: 2.2mm 4mm; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 3mm; }
  .rm-label { font-size: 2.1mm; font-weight: 700; color: #854d0e; white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .rm-items { display: flex; gap: 2mm; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .rm-item { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #fde047; border-radius: 5px; padding: 1mm 2.5mm; font-size: 2mm; color: #713f12; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1mm; }
  .rm-num { background:#fde047; color:#78350f; font-size:1.8mm; font-weight:700; border-radius:3px; padding:.2mm 1.2mm; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
  <div class="left">
    <div class="glow1"></div>
    <div class="glow2"></div>
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="brand-badge"><span>🏨</span><span>HotelScope</span></div>
      <h1>Hotel<em>Scope</em></h1>
      <p class="brand-desc">周辺ホテルの料金・評価・<br>需給データを自動収集し、<br><strong style="color:#f1f5f9">土地仕入れ判断</strong>を支援する<br>クラウド型市場調査システム</p>
      <span class="brand-tag">✦ 不動産仕入れ担当者専用ツール</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flow">
      <div class="sec-label">データ取得フロー</div>
      <div class="flow-steps">
        <div class="flow-step"><div class="fd b">📍</div><div class="ft"><strong>エリア指定（住所・駅名）</strong>半径 0.5〜10km・チェックイン日 指定</div></div>
        <div class="fa"></div>
        <div class="flow-step"><div class="fd g">🌏</div><div class="ft"><strong>ジオコーディング</strong>OpenStreetMap で緯度・経度に自動変換</div></div>
        <div class="fa"></div>
        <div class="flow-step"><div class="fd a">🔍</div><div class="ft"><strong>OTA 自動収集</strong>Booking.com 等から料金・評価を取得</div></div>
        <div class="fa"></div>
        <div class="flow-step"><div class="fd p">🤖</div><div class="ft"><strong>Gemini AI 投資分析</strong>ADR / RevPAR / 参入戦略を自動レポート化</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="lfoot">
      <div class="pills">
        <span class="pill">Next.js 14</span><span class="pill">FastAPI</span><span class="pill">Gemini AI</span>
        <span class="pill">Neon DB</span><span class="pill">Leaflet</span><span class="pill">Vercel</span>
      </div>
      <div class="url-line">🔗 hotelscope-frontend.vercel.app</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="right">
    <div class="rh">
      <div>
        <div class="rh-title">どのサイトを調査し、<em>何のデータ</em>を収集しているのか？</div>
        <div class="rh-sub">複数の OTA（ホテル予約サイト）から料金・評価を自動収集 → 5種の分析ビューで多角的に可視化</div>
      </div>
      <div class="client-box">
        <div class="cb-label">作成者</div>
        <div class="cb-name">開発チーム</div>
        <div class="cb-role">白井 様 向け資料 — 2026.05</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="sites-row">
      <div class="site-box"><span class="site-icon">🌐</span><span class="site-name">Booking.com</span><span class="site-status s-live">稼働中</span></div>
      <div class="site-box"><span class="site-icon">🏯</span><span class="site-name">じゃらん</span><span class="site-status s-soon">開発予定</span></div>
      <div class="site-box"><span class="site-icon">🍵</span><span class="site-name">一休.com</span><span class="site-status s-soon">開発予定</span></div>
      <div class="site-box"><span class="site-icon">🎴</span><span class="site-name">楽天トラベル</span><span class="site-status s-soon">開発予定</span></div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;padding:2.5mm 3mm;box-shadow:0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.06);">
        <div style="font-size:2.1mm;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin-bottom:1.5mm;">📦 収集するデータ項目（1ホテルあたり）</div>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.8mm 3mm;">
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ ホテル名（施設名称）</div>
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ 1泊料金（円建て）</div>
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ 評価スコア（10点満点）</div>
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ レビュー件数</div>
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ 位置情報（緯度・経度）</div>
          <div style="font-size:2mm;color:#374151;">▸ 予約ページ URL</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-blue"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">📊</span><span class="ct">概要タブ</span></div>
        <div class="cd">エリアの価格帯を瞬時に把握</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">調査ホテル件数・平均ADR</div>
          <div class="ci-row">最低価格 / 最高価格</div>
          <div class="ci-row">平日・休日・繁忙期 ADR 自動算出</div>
          <div class="ci-row">エリア平均評価スコア</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag tbl">平日比 休日+XX% 表示</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-rose"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">🏆</span><span class="ct">競合比較タブ</span></div>
        <div class="cd">周辺ホテルを横並びで比較</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">料金順・評価順でソート</div>
          <div class="ci-row">最大 20 件を一覧表示</div>
          <div class="ci-row">Booking.com 詳細ページへ直リンク</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag tro">クリックでソート</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-cyan"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">📅</span><span class="ct">価格推移タブ</span></div>
        <div class="cd">12ヶ月の季節変動をグラフ化</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">月別 平日 / 休日 / 繁忙期 ADR</div>
          <div class="ci-row">GW・夏休み・年末年始を自動反映</div>
          <div class="ci-row">棒グラフ + 数値テーブル併記</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag tcy">12 ヶ月自動生成</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-amber"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">📋</span><span class="ct">要因分析タブ</span></div>
        <div class="cd">需要変動の背景を自動解説</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">祝日・イベント（GW・花見 等）</div>
          <div class="ci-row">インバウンド動向・円安影響</div>
          <div class="ci-row">宿泊 CPI 上昇率（2024 年実績）</div>
          <div class="ci-row">天候・季節ノート（月別）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag tam">2024 / 2025 年対応</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-green"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">🗺️</span><span class="ct">地図タブ</span></div>
        <div class="cd">ホテル分布を地図で可視化</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">OpenStreetMap インタラクティブ地図</div>
          <div class="ci-row">調査エリア円（半径表示）</div>
          <div class="ci-row">各ホテルのピンマーカー</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags"><span class="tag tgn">半径サークル表示</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-bar bar-purple"></div>
        <div class="card-head"><span class="ci">🤖</span><span class="ct">AI 投資分析</span></div>
        <div class="cd">Gemini AI が投資判断レポートを生成</div>
        <div class="ci-list">
          <div class="ci-row">市場規模・競合環境の評価</div>
          <div class="ci-row">RevPAR 推定（稼働率 80%想定）</div>
          <div class="ci-row">投資リスク・機会・参入戦略</div>
        </div>
        <div class="tags">
          <span class="tag tpu">Gemini 1.5 Flash</span>
          <span class="tag tgr">500〜800字レポート</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="roadmap">
      <div class="rm-label">🚀 開発ロードマップ（白井様ご要望）</div>
      <div class="rm-items">
        <div class="rm-item"><span class="rm-num">①</span>じゃらん・一休・楽天 データ追加</div>
        <div class="rm-item"><span class="rm-num">②</span>Booking.com 実スクレイピング対応</div>
        <div class="rm-item"><span class="rm-num">③</span>過去データ蓄積・時系列グラフ比較</div>
        <div class="rm-item"><span class="rm-num">④</span>PDF 報告書 自動生成・一括出力</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>